LAHORE, Aug 17 (APP): Punjab Chief Minister Sardar Usman Buzdar has expressed deep sense of sorrow and grief over the loss of precious human lives due to overturning of boat in Keenjhar Lake.
In a message on Monday, the CM extended heartfelt sympathies to the bereaved family members and said, “We equally share the grief of the heirs of the deceased persons.”
